title: Worse Than You Think
description:
Your imagination can wreak havoc on your mind and soul. It can make you see and feel things that may not be real. But don’t ever let your guard down because if you’re not careful you’ll find out that things are far worse than you think.
First, influencers endanger themselves for the perfect post. 
Then, a fatal mistake by a sleepless neighbor. 
Followed by, a family vacation that becomes a family nightmare.
Finally in our final story, you may be done with the holidays, but they’re not done with you.
